Quest._questDescription: Robin, the local carpenter, lives north of town. In exchange for raw materials and money, she'll construct new buildings on your farm. You'll need her to build a coop or barn so that you can raise animals.

Quest._currentObjective: Reach Farming level 1 and craft a scarecrow.
Quest._questDescription: As you gain experience, you'll discover new crafting recipes to increase profit and make life easier. A scarecrow, for example, will prevent crows from snacking on your precious crops.

Wanted: Slime hunter to slay 6 Green Slimes in the local mine.
- 360g reward.
Quest.targetMessage: Ah, @! So you helped us with our slime problem? Thank you!$h#$b#I hope you didn't go through too much trouble... I know it can be really hard to get that sticky slime out your clothes.#$b# I've definitely ruined a few good pairs of pants trying to catch those little wigglers. I can remember Papa going into a rage after I got silvery slime all over my brand new silk pants... $h#$b# Well, anyways... enjoy your reward.

Quest._questDescription:
I'm running low on Iron Bar. If someone could bring me one, it would be much appreciated. - Elliott
- 360g on delivery. - Elliott will be thankful
Quest.targetMessage: Ah, the Iron Bar I requested! And it's a beautiful one, too. Thank you very much, Becca

Quest._questDescription: Robin lost her favorite axe. The last time she remembers using it, she was cutting wood south of Marnie's ranch.

Leah would like to hire someone to fetch Dandelion. You will be paid for your time.
- 120g on delivery. - Leah will be thankful
Quest.targetMessage: Oh! You brought me the item I asked for! Thanks so much!$h#$b# ...Let's see. Here's what I owe you.

Quest._questDescription: Jodi needs a fresh cauliflower for a recipe she's making. She's asking you to bring her one.
Quest.targetMessage: Oh, that looks so delicious! Thank you, this is just what I wanted. It's going to be perfect for my yellow curry.

Quest._currentObjective: Find and return Mayor Lewis' purple shorts.
Quest._questDescription: Mayor Lewis has lost his purple "shorts". He's asking you to find and return them... Discreetly.

Looking for a ripe Wheat. Could a local farmer deliver one to me? - Willy
- 75g on delivery. - Willy will be pleased
Quest.targetMessage: Oh! Is that the Wheat I requested? Thanks so much!$h#$b# Here's your payment, as promised.

Quest._questDescription: Pam is hankerin' for a pale ale. Regular old beer won't do. You can brew one yourself if you have hops and a keg.
Quest.targetMessage: Gimme that. *slurp*... Ahh, that's the stuff.#$b#It's real nice and hoppy... notes of citrus and pine, but with a robust body to keep it grounded.#$b#Thanks, kid. This means a lot to me. I knew I could count on you.$h

Quest._questDescription:
I will < you forever if you bring me Grape! -Haley
- 240g on delivery. - Makes Haley happy
Quest.targetMessage: Oh! That's exactly what I needed! Heehee! I'm so happy!$h

Quest._questDescription: Demetrius needs a fresh melon for his research.
Quest.targetMessage: This is perfect! It's just what I need for my research. It's going to be hard not to eat it! Thanks a bunch.

Quest._currentObjective: Reach the bottom of the mine.
Quest._questDescription: So far, there's no sign of the bottom. How low does it go?
George needs a hot pepper to soothe his aching knee.
Quest.targetMessage: Took you long enough... hmmph... Well it's good and spicy at least. Thanks.

Quest._currentObjective: Bring Marnie one bunch of amaranth.
Quest._questDescription: Marnie wants to give her cows a special treat. She's asking for a single bunch of amaranth.
Quest.targetMessage: Oh, the amaranth I asked for! Thank you so much... my cows are going to love this!$h

Quest._questDescription: Willy is challenging you to catch a squid. He says you can fish them from the ocean on winter nights.
Quest.targetMessage: Hey, you did it! Not bad. Not bad at all. I'm impressed.#$b#Winter's a good time to break out the old fishing rod, isn't it?

Quest._questDescription:
Buying 1 Earth Crystal at twice the market value! Please deliver directly to me. - Elliott
- 150g on delivery. - Makes Elliott happy
Quest.targetMessage: Ah, the Earth Crystal I requested! And it's a beautiful one, too. Thank you very much, Becca

Quest._questDescription: The wizard wants you to descend into the mines and fetch him a Void Essence. He needs it for some kind of dark magic.
Quest.targetMessage: Ah, you've brought it. You've earned my gratitude, and a 1000g reward. Now go.

Quest._questDescription:
I need Red Mushroom to rub on my sore hip.Please bring one as soon as you can! - Harvey
- 225g on delivery. - Harvey will be thankful
Quest.targetMessage: Hey! You brought me the item I asked for! I really appreciate it.$h#$b# ...Let's see. Here's what I owe you.

Quest._questDescription: Clint got a new hammer and he wants to test it out on a variety of metals.
Quest.targetMessage: Hey, it's the iron bar I asked for. It looks strong... perfect.#$b#Thanks, @. I appreciate this.

Quest._questDescription: Robin wrote to you asking for some hardwood.
Quest.targetMessage: Oh, you brought it! I know I can always count on you, @.$h#$b#Mmhmm... This wood is perfect. It's exactly what I need. Thanks!

Quest._questDescription: You encountered a suspicious looking figure by the bus stop. When it saw you, it fled toward town. Could there be a clue to its whereabouts?
Emily wants a taste of spring. She's asking for a fresh apricot.
Quest.targetMessage: Oh... You followed through! Thanks, this looks delicious!$h

Quest._questDescription: Evelyn wants to surprise her husband with a gift.
Quest.targetMessage: Oh, thank you, dear. This leek looks delicious. George will be so happy.#$b#He loves when I make eggs with leeks for breakfast.

Quest._questDescription: Giving gifts is a great way to build friendships. Learn each person's individual tastes and you'll be popular in no time.
